a Cricket and Football Club|Genova]]\n|team2 = Bologna\n|score = 1-1\n|report=\n|location = [[Genova]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Luigi Ferraris]]\n|referee = [[Gialma Bevilacqua|Bevilacqua]]\n|goals1 = [[Juan Esposto|Esposto]] {{Goal|23}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|49}} [[Bruno Maini|Maini]]\n|result=D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 2 February 1936\n|round = 17\n|team1 = Bologna\n|team2 = [[Fiorentina]]\n|score = 1-0\n|report=\n|location = [[Bologna]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Renato Dall'Ara|Stadio Littoriale]]\n|referee = [[Rinaldo Barlassina|Barlassina]]\n|goals1 = [[Raffaele Sansone|Sansone]] {{Goal|27}}\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 9 February 1936\n|round = 18\n|team1 = [[Inter Milan|Ambrosiana-Inter]]\n|team2 = Bologna\n|score = 3-1\n|report=\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = [[Gialma Bevilacqua|Bevilacqua]]\n|goals1 = [[Roberto Porta|Porta]] {{Goal|31|pen}}<br />[[Giuseppe Meazza|Meazza]] {{Goal|33}}<br />[[Attilio Demar\u00eda|Demar\u00eda]] {{Goal|38}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|11}} [[Raffaele Sansone|Sansone]]\n|result=L\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 16 February 1936\n|round = 19\n|team1 = Bologna\n|team2 = [[S.S.C. Napoli|Napoli]]\n|score = 2-1\n|report=\n|location = [[Bologna]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Renato Dall'Ara|Stadio Littoriale]]\n|referee = Lelio Salvatori\n|goals1 = [[Bruno Maini|Maini]] {{Goal|33}}<br />[[Gerardo Ottani|Ottani]] {{Goal|55}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|50}} [[Carlo Buscaglia|Buscaglia]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 23 February 1936\n|round = 20\n|team1 = Bologna\n|team2 = [[Juventus]]\n|score = 2-1\n|report=\n|location = [[Bologna]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Renato Dall'Ara|Stadio Littoriale]]\n|referee = [[Gino Mazzarini|Mazzarini]]\n|goals1 = [[Angelo Schiavio|Schiavio]] {{Goal|25}}<br />[[Gerardo Ottani|Ottani]] {{Goal|36}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|43}} [[Guglielmo Gabetto|Gabetto]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 1 March 1936\n|round = 21\n|team1 = [[Brescia Calcio