ini|Maini]] {{Goal|64}}\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 19 April 1936\n|round = 27\n|team1 = [[S.S. Lazio|Lazio]]\n|team2 = Bologna\n|score = 1-1\n|report=\n|location = [[Rome|Roma]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Nazionale PNF|Stadio Nazionale del PNF]]\n|referee = Angelo Gianelli\n|goals1 = [[Luigi Uneddu|Uneddu]] {{Goal|27}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|39}} [[Angelo Schiavio|Schiavio]]\n|result=D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 26 April 1936\n|round = 28\n|team1 = Bari\n|team2 = Bologna\n|score = 0-0\n|report=\n|location = [[Bari]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio della Vittoria (Bari)|Stadio della Vittoria]]\n|referee = Giuseppe Scarpi\n|result=D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 3 May 1936\n|round = 29\n|team1 = Bologna\n|team2 = Palermo\n|score = 1-0\n|report=\n|location = [[Bologna]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Renato Dall'Ara|Stadio Littoriale]]\n|referee = Pompeo Casati\n|result=W\n|goals1 = [[Michele Andreolo|Andreolo]] {{Goal|47}}\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 10 May 1936\n|round = 30\n|team1 = Bologna\n|team2 = Triestina\n|score = 3-0\n|report=\n|location = [[Bologna]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Renato Dall'Ara|Stadio Littoriale]]\n|referee = Angelo Gianelli\n|goals1 = [[Michele Andreolo|Andreolo]] {{Goal|11}}<br />[[Angelo Schiavio|Schiavio]] {{Goal|46}}<br />[[Nereo Rocco|Rocco]] {{Goal|64|aut.}}\n|result=W\n}}\n\n=== Coppa Italia ===\n{{main|1935-36 Coppa Italia}}\n==== Round of 32 ====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 25 December 1935\n|team1 = Bologna\n|team2 = Novara\n|score = 1-0\n|report=\n|location = [[Bologna]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Renato Dall'Ara|Stadio Littoriale]]\n|referee = Alfredo Conticini\n|goals1 = [[Alcide Ivan Violi|Violi]] {{Goal|30}}\n|goals2=\n|result=W\n}}\n\n==== Eightfinals ====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 19 January 1936\n|team1 = [[A.C. Milan|Milan]]\n|team2 = Bologna\n|score = 3-0\n|report=\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Giuseppe Meazza|San Siro]]\n|referee= Giuseppe Scarpi\n|goals1 = [[Pietro Arcari|Arcari III]] {{Goal|53||71}}<br />[[Giovanni Moretti|Moretti]] {{Goal|64}}\n|goals2=\n|result=L\n}}\n\n=== Mitropa Cup ===\n{{main|Mitropa Cup}}\n==== Eightfinals ====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 21 June 1936\n|team1 = Bologna\n|team2 = {{flagicon|AUT}}[[Austria Wien]]\n|score = 2-1\n|report=\n|location = [[Bologna]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Renato Dall'Ara|Stadio Littoriale]]\n|referee = {{flagicon|CZE}}Br\u00fcll\n|goals1 = [[Bruno Maini|Maini]] {{Goal|6}}<br />[[Angelo Schiavio|Schiavio]] {{Goal|21}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|77}} [[Rudolf Viertl|Viertl]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 28 June 1936\n|team1 = {{flagicon|AUT}}[[Austria Wien]]\n|team2 = Bologna\n|score = 4-0\n|report=\n|location = [[Wien]]\n|stadium = [[Ernst Happel Stadion|Prater]]\n|referee = {{flagicon|HUN}}Mih\u00e1ly Iv\u00e1ncsics\n|goals1 = [[Camillo Jerusalem|Jerusalem]] {{Goal|12||90}}<br />[[Josef Stroh|Stroh]] {{Goal|31}}<br />[[Matthias Sindelar|Sindelar]] {{Goal|87}}\n|goals2=\n|result=L\n}}\n\n== Statistics ==\n=== Squad statistics ===\n<div style=\"font-size:90%\">\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;margin:auto;clear:both;text-align:center;\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Competition<ref>{{cite book|publisher=Panini|title=1936|p=94}}.</ref>\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Points\n! colspan=\"6\" | Home\n! colspan=\"6\" | Away\n! colspan=\"6\" | Total\n! rowspan=\"2\" | [[Goal average|GD]]\n|-\n! {{Descrizione comando|G|Games}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|W|Won}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|D|Draw}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|L|Lost}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|Gs|Goals scored}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|Ga|Goals against}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|G|Games}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|W|Won}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|D|Draw}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|L|Lost}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|Gs|Goals scored}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|Ga|Goals against}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|G|Games}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|W|Won}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|D|Draw}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|L|Lost}}\n! {{Descrizione coman